00:05.273 --> 00:06.440
Friday night?

00:06.540 --> 00:08.109
I don't know
if it's gonna work.

00:08.209 --> 00:10.010
PEPPER:
People have been talking.

00:10.111 --> 00:12.880
Something they heard about that
happened at your old school?

00:12.980 --> 00:16.217
You ever have one of those cases
that keep you awake at night?

00:16.317 --> 00:17.685
This one's mine.

00:17.785 --> 00:19.853
Ryan Winter.

00:19.953 --> 00:21.789
D:
Fucking Hynes is obsessed.

00:21.889 --> 00:23.857
Whole timeline on his wall
about murder

00:23.957 --> 00:26.026
and where this Winter
was when.

00:26.127 --> 00:28.262
CHANCE:
You broke in to his place?

00:28.362 --> 00:32.600
I'm gonna need you to get into
Ryan Winter's head for me.

00:32.700 --> 00:35.303
I have some pictures
that I'd like to show you.

00:35.403 --> 00:37.705
Tell me what you see.

00:37.805 --> 00:39.940
Josefa, how's it going?

00:40.040 --> 00:41.709
He caught me
wearing makeup.

00:41.809 --> 00:43.411
My husband, Ronny.

00:43.511 --> 00:44.778
CHANCE:
I'm looking for Josefa Pefaur.

00:44.878 --> 00:46.947
I'm her psychiatrist.

00:47.047 --> 00:47.981
We had an appointment.
She didn't show.

00:48.082 --> 00:49.583
Is she inside?
Is she okay?

00:49.683 --> 00:52.153
OFFICER: I need you to go back
downstairs, sir,

00:52.253 --> 00:53.287
right now.

