06:23.083 --> 06:25.653
**

06:25.753 --> 06:28.221
What if it was this Ronny?

06:28.321 --> 06:30.223
Why is that so crazy?
The guy's a shit stain.

06:30.323 --> 06:32.726
No, this was Winter, D.

06:32.826 --> 06:35.395
If you'd seen the way
he's zeroed in on Josefa --

06:35.496 --> 06:39.767
Not because he was commiserating
or sharing out of empathy.

06:39.867 --> 06:42.570
Hard-ons aren't a gateway drug
for murder.

06:42.670 --> 06:43.837
We know Winter's
a sick piece of shit.

06:43.937 --> 06:47.140
Does Ronny really have
an alibi?

06:47.240 --> 06:50.310
Yes, actually, he does.

06:50.410 --> 06:55.616
**

06:55.716 --> 06:57.685
You ever have
one of those moments

06:57.785 --> 07:01.489
where, suddenly,
everything makes sense?

07:01.589 --> 07:02.956
**

07:06.193 --> 07:12.165
**

07:12.265 --> 07:14.702
Fuck me.

07:14.802 --> 07:16.303
You know
what would be interesting

07:16.403 --> 07:18.839
is if we were compare
this shit

07:18.939 --> 07:22.209
to the coroner's report
on Blackstone.

07:22.309 --> 07:24.177
Depth of cuts,
nature of wounds

07:24.277 --> 07:26.346
as in what caused them --

07:26.446 --> 07:28.616
single blade, double blade,

07:28.716 --> 07:32.520
serrated edge,
curved versus straight.

07:32.620 --> 07:35.889
Hell, I'd say you pretty much
have them all covered here.

07:35.989 --> 07:37.357
**

07:37.457 --> 07:39.459
And here, I thought
I'd found a pal.

07:39.560 --> 07:42.329
I saw a soul in distress.

07:42.429 --> 07:43.497
You had
my sympathies,

07:43.597 --> 07:44.665
and you still do.

07:44.765 --> 07:45.633
Save it, Pops.

07:45.733 --> 07:47.635
**

07:47.735 --> 07:52.072
You know, I remember what was
bugging me at the bar now.

07:52.172 --> 07:54.675
You're that natty,
older gentleman

07:54.775 --> 07:56.043
who crashed his car

07:56.143 --> 08:00.013
into some Romanians
out at the beach.

08:00.113 --> 08:02.516
Manny, Moe, and Jack.

08:02.616 --> 08:07.921
So, what's that make you?
A dirty, blackmailing cop.

08:08.021 --> 08:14.094
**

08:14.194 --> 08:17.531
Josefa Pefaur.

08:17.631 --> 08:18.732
What the hell
does that mean?

08:18.832 --> 08:19.933
She was a patient of mine
at the clinic.

08:20.033 --> 08:21.869
She was murdered
in her apartment.

08:21.969 --> 08:23.236
I was at the crime scene.

08:23.336 --> 08:24.938
I got a glimpse
of the body.

08:25.038 --> 08:27.941
It was posed to mimic a drawing
that I had shown Winter.

08:28.041 --> 08:29.743
He reacted
to something in her story,

08:29.843 --> 08:31.044
and then
the drawing provoked

08:31.144 --> 08:34.181
something
he couldn't articulate.

08:34.281 --> 08:40.120
**

08:40.220 --> 08:41.388
So, what now?

08:41.488 --> 08:45.392
How about now,
Winter goes away?

08:45.492 --> 08:47.394
Meaning what, exactly?

08:47.494 --> 08:49.563
Meaning somebody stabs him
in the fucking eye.

08:49.663 --> 08:52.766
He goes away
when I say he goes away,

08:52.866 --> 08:55.535
in the court of law
where I can see it.

08:55.636 --> 08:58.271
Now, if you've got a problem
with that, say so right now.

08:58.371 --> 09:00.207
He doesn't.
Neither do I.

09:00.307 --> 09:01.609
Well, fantastic.

09:01.709 --> 09:02.776
So, where do we start?

09:02.876 --> 09:04.578
**

09:04.678 --> 09:06.379
(horn honks in distance)

09:07.648 --> 09:09.382
Well, first thing is
that I have to keep Winter

09:09.482 --> 09:10.584
out of the clinic.

09:10.684 --> 09:12.953
Your problem is that the cops
decided to hang this

09:13.053 --> 09:14.321
on Josefa's husband, Ronny.

09:14.421 --> 09:15.488
He has an alibi,

09:15.589 --> 09:17.625
but no one seems that inclined
to believe it.

09:17.725 --> 09:18.726
Well, did he tell you
what it was?

09:18.826 --> 09:20.794
I believe it.

09:20.894 --> 09:23.063
**

09:23.163 --> 09:27.434
Well, I have Legal Aid lawyer
who actually owes me a favor,

09:27.534 --> 09:28.802
and he'll actually
be jazzed

09:28.936 --> 09:30.604
to have a client
who didn't do it.

09:30.704 --> 09:33.273
I'll call him tomorrow
because tonight,

09:33.373 --> 09:38.011
we're gonna go corroborate
the husband's alibi.

09:38.111 --> 09:39.012
**

09:39.112 --> 09:41.014
And if you're riding along,
big fella,

09:41.114 --> 09:42.983
know this...
(coin clinks)

09:43.083 --> 09:44.417
**

09:44.517 --> 09:46.486
You ever break
into my apartment again,

09:46.586 --> 09:49.857
I'll stab you
in the fucking eye.

09:49.957 --> 09:52.359
**

09:52.459 --> 09:54.527
(footsteps)

09:54.628 --> 09:57.831
**

09:57.931 --> 10:00.968
**

10:01.068 --> 10:03.704
**

10:03.804 --> 10:07.107
Hey, Nicole!
Nicole!

10:07.207 --> 10:09.877
Hey. Didn't you
hear me calling you?

10:09.977 --> 10:11.945
Guess not.

10:12.045 --> 10:14.514
I feel really bad about
what happened with Jason.

10:14.614 --> 10:16.116
It's not about him.

10:16.216 --> 10:17.718
Well, still, whatever.

10:17.818 --> 10:19.687
He didn't have to be
such a dick about it.

10:21.021 --> 10:24.024
My advice?
Just move on.

10:24.124 --> 10:25.325
Forget about it.
Seriously.

10:25.425 --> 10:26.994
Just like
it never even happened.

10:27.094 --> 10:28.996
How can I?

10:29.096 --> 10:33.466
It followed me here,
and it's all over the Internet.

10:33.566 --> 10:36.069
I can't believe I have to live
with this forever.

10:38.005 --> 10:40.674
And, you know, what pisses me
off more than anything

10:40.774 --> 10:44.411
is that all anyone cares about
is John's side of the story.

10:44.511 --> 10:46.814
Nobody even asks me
for mine.

10:46.914 --> 10:48.048
I'm not a psycho.

10:48.148 --> 10:50.517
Look. I get it.

10:50.617 --> 10:53.086
We have all done
dumb shit over guys before.

10:53.186 --> 10:54.487
(chuckles)

10:54.587 --> 10:57.590
So your shit just got
a little bit dumber.

10:57.691 --> 10:59.659
Who cares?
Trust me.

10:59.760 --> 11:01.528
In two days,
everybody will be on

11:01.628 --> 11:04.231
to somebody else's
dumb shit, okay?

11:04.331 --> 11:06.033
Okay.

11:06.133 --> 11:07.701
Hey. Uh.

11:07.801 --> 11:09.202
Let's go get some pizza.

11:09.302 --> 11:12.940
(indistinct conversations)

11:13.040 --> 11:14.742
Come on.

11:14.842 --> 11:16.543
Okay.
(chuckles)

11:16.643 --> 11:18.545
(conversations continue)

11:18.645 --> 11:21.548
(A Tribe Called Red's
"Electric Pow Wow" plays)

11:21.648 --> 11:23.250
(chanting)

11:28.756 --> 11:31.358
(music continues on radio)

11:31.458 --> 11:32.625
What is this shit?

11:32.726 --> 11:34.728
What?

11:34.828 --> 11:36.596
What is this shit?!

11:36.696 --> 11:38.098
It's his music.

11:38.198 --> 11:39.366
(chanting continues)

11:39.466 --> 11:40.600
(button clicks, music stops)

11:40.700 --> 11:42.903
What the fuck
are you doing?

11:43.003 --> 11:44.738
Look, I'm not gonna sit here
and listen

11:44.838 --> 11:46.706
to "The Best of Cries
from Hell."

11:46.807 --> 11:47.908
What the fuck?

11:48.008 --> 11:50.443
Look, Doc, I don't know
if you need Sitting Bull here

11:50.543 --> 11:51.812
to tag along, but I don't.

11:51.912 --> 11:53.446
Keep talking, asshole.

11:53.546 --> 11:54.915
You're about five seconds away

11:55.015 --> 11:56.483
from the most humiliating moment
of your life.

11:56.583 --> 11:58.819
Listen to me,
you big fuck.

11:58.919 --> 12:01.321
I got no problem
pulling the car over right now

12:01.421 --> 12:03.256
and putting a bullet
in your fucking head.

12:03.356 --> 12:04.992
Fantastic.

12:05.092 --> 12:07.127
There's a dump site a quarter
of a mile up on the right.

12:07.227 --> 12:08.661
You can do it there.

12:08.762 --> 12:10.764
That way, I can bury your body
after I --

12:10.864 --> 12:12.732
Jesus Christ!

12:12.833 --> 12:15.002
(tires screech)

12:15.102 --> 12:17.604
Get the fuck
out of this car.

12:17.704 --> 12:19.739
Let's go.

12:19.840 --> 12:21.174
Guns on the hood.

12:22.976 --> 12:25.078
(horn honks in distance)

12:28.581 --> 12:30.350
**

12:30.450 --> 12:31.618
(clanking)

12:31.718 --> 12:34.788
**

12:34.888 --> 12:36.857
(clanking)

12:36.957 --> 12:41.528
**

12:41.628 --> 12:44.597
**

12:44.697 --> 12:48.168
Will you two
just fucking knock it off?!

12:48.268 --> 12:49.636
Listen.

12:49.736 --> 12:51.638
I'm here
because you need me.

12:51.738 --> 12:53.440
He's here
because I need him.

12:53.540 --> 12:56.043
Now, let's all just take
a deep fucking breath

12:56.143 --> 12:58.946
and go do what we came to do.

12:59.046 --> 13:01.381
This ain't over.

13:01.481 --> 13:03.516
I mean, how the fuck

13:03.616 --> 13:09.122
you're not doing life
without parole is beyond me.

13:09.222 --> 13:11.191
Come on.
Let's go.

13:11.291 --> 13:12.292
(footsteps)

13:12.392 --> 13:14.394
(car door opens)

13:14.494 --> 13:17.330
How do you lead this fuck-nut
to my place?

13:17.430 --> 13:18.899
I know.
I'm sorry.

13:18.999 --> 13:20.300
**

13:20.400 --> 13:24.071
You put it all in jeopardy,
everything we've done.

13:24.171 --> 13:27.007
Just remember that
when shit goes south.

13:27.107 --> 13:28.375
**

13:28.475 --> 13:32.712
(Latin hip-hop music plays)

13:32.812 --> 13:35.482
(man singing in Spanish)

13:35.582 --> 13:39.819
**

13:39.920 --> 13:44.824
**

13:44.925 --> 13:47.160
(valve squeaks)

13:47.260 --> 13:49.229
**

13:49.329 --> 13:51.498
(speaking Spanish)
(music stops)

14:09.782 --> 14:11.851
Look, nobody's gonna get
in trouble.

14:11.952 --> 14:13.753
All's I need you to say

14:13.853 --> 14:17.424
is that you were here two nights
ago with Ronny, that's all.

14:19.927 --> 14:22.529
Let's just say he's gonna
be gone quite a while.

14:22.629 --> 14:23.596
**

