15:55.088 --> 15:56.056
Josefa Pefaur.

15:56.156 --> 15:59.659
**

15:59.759 --> 16:01.894
Josefa Pefaur...

16:01.995 --> 16:04.131
(gasps)
Oh, the Brillo-pad woman?

16:04.231 --> 16:06.366
Uh-huh.

16:06.466 --> 16:08.368
I am so sorry
to hear that.

16:08.468 --> 16:11.638
She seemed nice.

16:11.738 --> 16:13.240
**

16:13.340 --> 16:17.210
As I recall, you two talked
quite extensively.

16:17.310 --> 16:19.679
Yeah.

16:19.779 --> 16:22.849
Misery loves company.

16:22.949 --> 16:26.053
That's an interesting way
to sum up a life.

16:26.153 --> 16:29.089
Oh, I-I wasn't trying
to be glib.

16:29.189 --> 16:30.357
**

16:30.457 --> 16:33.060
You seem more relaxed
than when we last spoke.

16:33.160 --> 16:36.063
**

16:36.163 --> 16:38.865
Must be the massage I got
last night.

16:38.965 --> 16:41.334
**

16:41.434 --> 16:43.070
In any case,
group is canceled today

16:43.170 --> 16:47.107
