of Josefa's death.

16:47.207 --> 16:48.341
You want to take a walk,
you and me?

16:48.441 --> 16:49.876
You -- Uh, did you say
group was canceled?

16:49.976 --> 16:51.111
Uh-huh.
Okay.

16:51.211 --> 16:53.880
Nobody mentioned anything
about that.

16:53.980 --> 16:55.848
Well,
I'm mentioning it now.

16:55.948 --> 16:57.684
**

16:57.784 --> 17:00.453
