17:00.553 --> 17:02.422
Okay, sure.

17:02.522 --> 17:04.624
Do you want to wait for me
in the lobby?

17:04.724 --> 17:06.426
I just got to make
a quick call.

17:06.526 --> 17:10.063
Yes.
Take your time.

