17:26.879 --> 17:28.881
CHANCE:
Winter is here in my office,

17:28.981 --> 17:30.750
cool
as a fucking cucumber.

17:30.850 --> 17:31.751
No shit.

17:31.851 --> 17:33.720
Why wouldn't he be,
he's the psycho you say?

17:33.820 --> 17:35.122
But there's something
I noticed --

17:35.222 --> 17:37.124
change rattles him.

17:37.224 --> 17:40.293
It's pretty common
in obsessive-compulsives,

17:40.393 --> 17:42.895
but it might be something
we can use --

17:42.995 --> 17:44.063
some way of disrupting
his routine,

17:44.164 --> 17:45.998
getting under his skin.
Gaslight the fucker.

17:46.099 --> 17:47.400
**

17:47.500 --> 17:50.137
If I keep him here,
can you get into his house?

17:50.237 --> 17:53.606
