25:10.142 --> 25:11.844
This is Barry Gilyard.

25:11.944 --> 25:12.879
He's our
chief investigator.

25:12.979 --> 25:13.913
I've been telling them

25:15.147 --> 25:15.548
about the outstanding progress
you were making with Josefa.

25:15.648 --> 25:18.551
Yeah.

25:18.651 --> 25:21.788
Yeah, it's, uh --
it's very sad.

25:21.888 --> 25:24.090
She was really starting
to take control of her life.

25:24.190 --> 25:25.524
Well, I'm sorry
that we can't be meeting

25:25.625 --> 25:27.927
under better circumstances,
but the good news is

25:28.027 --> 25:31.864
we just charged Ronaldo Pefaur
with the murder of his wife,

25:31.964 --> 25:34.266
so I'll be prosecuting
that case personally.

25:34.366 --> 25:36.803
And I promise you,
we'll pull out all the stops.

25:38.437 --> 25:40.707
So, Ronny's alibi
didn't check out?

25:40.807 --> 25:41.708
They rarely do.

25:42.709 --> 25:44.644
The reason that we --
we wanted to talk to you

25:44.744 --> 25:45.912
was to see if you could
give us any information

25:46.012 --> 25:48.380
about Josefa's relationship,

25:48.480 --> 25:50.750
uh, from a doctor-patient
perspective.

25:50.850 --> 25:54.553
Well, obviously, we know that
he was a serial abuser, so...

25:54.654 --> 25:56.455
Ronny Pefaur
had a history of assault.

25:56.555 --> 26:00.226
He's got multiple arrests,
some prison time,

26:00.326 --> 26:04.096
but Josefa never said
he used a weapon against her.

26:04.196 --> 26:08.100
Why would he suddenly
attack her with a knife?

26:08.200 --> 26:09.168
Well,
sometimes a perpetrator,

26:10.369 --> 26:11.137
when they feel they're not
making enough of an impression,

26:11.237 --> 26:13.305
they take it
to the next level.

26:13.405 --> 26:15.975
A foot-and-fist guy
goes and gets a knife.

26:16.075 --> 26:18.310
A knife guy
might go and get a gun.

26:18.410 --> 26:20.613
We call it
"conflict escalation."

26:20.713 --> 26:21.814
So do we.

26:21.914 --> 26:23.449
GILYARD:
This happens all the time,

26:23.549 --> 26:24.516
just like the accused

26:24.617 --> 26:25.685
trying to finger
somebody else.

26:26.919 --> 26:27.987
But this guy's hitting
on all the dirtbag landmarks.
Yeah.

26:28.087 --> 26:30.857
Ronny's tried to put this
on someone else? Who?

26:30.957 --> 26:33.425
He's floating a story about
being on a bus

26:33.525 --> 26:35.327
and seeing his wife walking
with some white guy,

26:35.427 --> 26:37.296
but by the time he got
off of the bus,

26:37.396 --> 26:38.530
they were gone, of course.

26:38.631 --> 26:39.632
So you don't believe him?

26:39.732 --> 26:40.833
No, sure I do.

26:40.933 --> 26:43.035
Also, Nicole Brown Simpson
was murdered

26:43.135 --> 26:44.303
by Colombian drug dealers.

26:44.403 --> 26:45.938
Okay.
(Kirsten clears throat)

26:46.038 --> 26:47.473
Look, I just want to say

26:47.573 --> 26:49.676
I-I know you don't hear this
from City Hall enough,

26:49.776 --> 26:50.810
but you guys here

26:50.910 --> 26:53.946
are one of the few
absolute goods in this world,

26:54.046 --> 26:55.314
so, I know it's tough,

26:55.414 --> 26:57.383
but keep on doing
what you're doing.

26:57.483 --> 27:01.020
That's kind of you to say.

27:01.120 --> 27:03.322
And we should go.

27:03.422 --> 27:06.793
Thank you for your time.
(clears throat)

27:08.995 --> 27:09.896
-Thank you.
-We'll be in touch.

27:09.996 --> 27:10.997
Thank you.

