28:48.761 --> 28:50.262
I don't know.
It's weird.

28:50.362 --> 28:51.597
But I met her,
like, one time,

28:51.697 --> 28:52.832
then you know
how it is --

28:52.932 --> 28:53.933
All of a sudden,
they want to be

28:54.033 --> 28:55.134
best friends
on social media

28:55.234 --> 28:57.403
and all that bullshit.

28:57.503 --> 28:59.105
