28:59.205 --> 29:01.307
YOUNG MAN: Okay, cool.

29:01.407 --> 29:02.674
You did it.

29:02.775 --> 29:04.410
**

29:04.510 --> 29:05.611
W-- Did what?

29:05.711 --> 29:07.914
You spread that shit around
about me and John.

29:08.014 --> 29:10.516
Dude,
what are you talking about?

29:10.616 --> 29:13.485
You know
what I'm talking about.

29:13.585 --> 29:15.822
Why would you do that
to me?

29:15.922 --> 29:17.623
Okay, Nicole, just --
Why would you tell
everybody?

29:17.723 --> 29:19.792
Nicole, chill out.

29:19.892 --> 29:20.927
And then just sit here,
acting like my friend?

29:21.027 --> 29:21.961
Dude, chill out.
You're making a --

29:22.061 --> 29:22.995
You are not my friend!

29:23.095 --> 29:25.531
You are an asshole.

29:25.631 --> 29:26.532
(scoffs)

29:26.632 --> 29:30.202
(laughter)

29:30.302 --> 29:32.604
Whatever,
stalker freak.

29:32.704 --> 29:36.608
(laughter)

