29:56.963 --> 30:00.066
How many fucking times
do I have to say it?

30:00.166 --> 30:02.401
I did not kill her.

30:02.501 --> 30:03.970
Well,
they think you did.

30:04.070 --> 30:05.171
RONNY: Yeah.

30:05.271 --> 30:06.973
We got to change
